In the last sentence, Andrej is explaining the preliminary steps that he completed for the tutorial on understanding and appreciating how ChatGPT works. This includes creating a new Google Colab Jupyter notebook, which will be shared in the video description to help viewers follow along with his explanations. Additionally, Andrej downloaded the 'Tiny Shakespeare' dataset, which is a 1-megabyte file containing all the works of Shakespeare. He explains that this dataset will be used to train a Transformer-based language model, a fundamental component of ChatGPT.